        "content": [
          "Three words for 'when' with different uses:",
          "",
          "WANN (questions):",
          "Used for direct and indirect questions:",
          "",
          "Wann kommst du? (When are you coming?)",
          "Ich weiß nicht, wann er kommt.",
          "(I don't know when he's coming)",
          "",
          "ALS (one-time past event):",
          "Als ich Kind war... (When I was a child...)",
          "Als er ankam... (When he arrived...)",
          "",
          "WENN (repeated events or future):",
          "Wenn ich Zeit habe... (Whenever I have time...)",
          "Wenn er kommt... (When/If he comes...)",
          "",
          "Think: WANN = question, ALS = once in past,",
          "WENN = repeated or future"
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion 60"
      }
